section.t:
Consortiums also need to establish guidelines for each participating provider to adhere. The RECOMMENDED guidelines include:
Physical and logical practices to protect GRC-Exchange systems;
Network and application layer protection for GRC-Exchange systems and communications;
Proper use guidelines for GRC-Exchange systems, messages, and requests; and
A PKI, certificate policy, and certification practices statement to provide authentication, integrity, and privacy.

